        </div>
        <div class="js-tooltipTrigger tooltipTrigger" data-resource-type='Book' data-resource-id='11437' data-placement='bottom-left'>
          <a href="/book/show/11437.Where_I_m_Calling_From"><img id="more_book_11437" alt="Where I&#39;m Calling From: New and Selected Stories" title="Where I&#39;m Calling From: New and Selected Stories" width="50" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388237827l/11437._SX98_.jpg" /></a>
